<HEADLINE> Three Nepalese Arrested for Heroin Smuggling </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Customs officials at Lahore
Thursday arrested three Nepalese and foiled their bid to smuggle
two kilograms of white heroin of fine quality from Lahore to New
Delhi through Wagha border.
</P>
