supportive to China's stand on Taiwan, Tibet and human rights.
</P>
<P>
King Birendra made the remarks while meeting with a visiting
goodwill military delegation of the Chinese People's Liberation
Army (PLA) led by Lt. Gen. Li Jinai, political commissar of the
PLA's General Armament Department.
</P>
<P>
The king said that friendship between Nepal and China is
time-honored and the Nepalese government and people are grateful
to the assistance provided by the Chinese government and people.
</P>
<P>
