cordial greetings to Chinese President Jiang Zemin.
</P>
<P>
On the occasion, Li conveyed best regards from President Jiang
to King Birendra.
</P>
<P>
He said that there are no problems existing between the two
neighbors, and China is ready, through joint efforts with Nepal,
to bring the good-neighborly relations into the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
He said that South Asia is an important component of Asia; Asia
as a whole cannot have peace and development without peace and
stability in South Asia.
</P>
<P>
China sincerely hopes that bilateral disputes are resolved
through dialog and negotiations so as to develop economy and raise
the living standard of the peoples thereby, he stressed.
</P>
<P>
The six-member Chinese military delegation arrived here
Wednesday evening for a five-day visit.
</P>
<P>
The delegation had visited Pakistan and Bangladesh and will
visit Myanmar after the Nepal tour. 
