<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Roundup: In Search of a Peaceful Environment (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The establishment of a strategic cooperative partnership
oriented toward the 21st century, as well as enhanced consultation
and cooperation in all fields, are of far reaching influence in
promoting not only friendly bilateral ties but also peace and
stability in the region and the world at large, as both sides
agreed.
</P>
<P>
Analysts here pointed out that Zhang's current visit, the first
by a senior Chinese military leader to Russia since the
presidential summit last year, is a major step toward the
establishment of their strategic cooperative partnership.
</P>
<P>
People have the reason to believe that the military meetings
between these two major countries, which bear major responsibility
for maintaining world peace and are two permanent members of the
UN Security Council, will help unite with peace loving forces in
the world and promote the cause of peace throughout the world.
</P>
<P>
Security comes through interaction. Thus, maintaining and
developing healthy and stable bilateral ties is a practical
approach for assuring regional peace and security, as is
strengthening military exchanges. 
</P>
