<HEADLINE> Fresh Fighting Kills 10 Tamil Rebels in Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan government troops
Wednesday killed 10 Tamil rebels in separate clashes in the
northern Jaffna area, the Defense Ministry announced Thursday.
</P>
