substances in the first three months of this year, the Australian
Sports Drug Agency said in Sydney on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Of the last eight positive tests, Olympic baseball player Shane
Hogan received a two-year ban for testing positive to the steroid
stanozolol.
</P>
<P>
