Two unnamed powerlifters were banned for three years and two
disabled swimmers received warnings after testing positive for the
stimulant salbutamol.
</P>
<P>
The eighth positive test was returned by an unnamed soccer
player who tested positive to pseudoephedrine in January and has
yet to be sanctioned.
</P>
<P>
No foreign athletes training or competing in Australia tested
positive during the latest three-month period, the agency said.
