the Lawyers College, "La Plata," said that some Belgian foodstuffs
have been contaminated with dioxin, a toxic substance that could
cause cancer, weaken the body's immune system, alter hormone
production, and possibly cause malformations in embryos. (
LAmerica-Belgian Food-Warning)
</P>
