project is estimated at 226 million yuan (about 27 million U.S.
dollars), he said, adding that all the World Bank money will be
directed to 15 poverty-stricken counties.
</P>
<P>
The previous two batches of World Bank loans and their
counterpart funds for the specially designed projects, with a
combined value of more than 600 million yuan (some 72 million U.S.
dollars), have been used to plant trees on more than 100,000
hectares of land, the official said.  
