<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Results of Heineken Trophy Tennis Tourney </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, June 16 (Xinhua) -- Following are the second round
results from Heineken Trophy combined $475,000 ATP men's and $180,
000 WTA women's grass-court tennis tournament in Den Bosch, the
Netherlands, on Wednesday (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Men
