<HEADLINE> Steaua Bucharest Wins Romanian Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, June 16 (Xinhua) -- Steaua Bucharest beat Rapid
Bucharest 6-4 in a penalty shootout on Wednesday to win the soccer
Romanian Cup final after the sides drew 2-2 in 120 minutes.
</P>
<P>
After the goalless first half, Cristian Ciocoiu opened the
scoring for Steaua in the 67th minute.
</P>
