<HEADLINE> Argentine Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, June 16 (Xinhua) -- The leading Merval index of
the Buenos Aires Stock Exchange rose 2.52 percent to 518.14 points
on Wednesday.
